    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Occurrences of moving masses of soil made fluid by rain or melting snow, or masses of mingled volcanic particles and water that flow like lava from volcanoes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000042061/Webster's Third New International Dictionary (1961)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Movimiento de masas de suelo convertidas en fluido como consecuencia de la lluvia o a la nieve derretida, o bien masas de partículas volcánicas mezcladas y agua que mana de los volcanes como la lava.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
